[SHORT DESC]
Picks one of the user's moves at random. Can only be used while sleeping.

[LONG DESC]
<p>Picks one of the user's moves at random. Can only be used while sleeping. The following moves cannot be chosen by Sleep Talk:</p>

<ul>
<li>Assist</li>
<li>Bide</li>
<li>Bounce</li>
<li>Dig</li>
<li>Dive</li>
<li>Fly</li>
<li>Focus Punch</li>
<li>Metronome</li>
<li>Mirror Move</li>
<li>Skull Bash</li>
<li>Sky Attack</li>
<li>Sleep Talk</li>
<li>SolarBeam</li>
<li>Razor Wind</li>
<li>Uproar</li>
<li>Any move the user cannot choose for use</li>
</ul>

<p>No PP is spent for the move used. If Sleep Talk selects Blast Burn, Frenzy Plant, Hydro Cannon, or Hyper Beam, Sleep Talk loses 1 PP when using the move, and if the user remains asleep next turn, Sleep Talk is forced to be selected for the recharge turn and loses another PP.</p>

<p>If Sleep Talk selects Ice Ball or Rollout in consecutive turns, they are not boosted.</p>